item.dc:creator: @Kodiak Kodiak
item.description:
@Kodiak wrote:

If your on jre7 change your run.bat from ‘java blah blah blah’ to “C:/Program Files (x86)/Java/jre7/bin/java.exe” blah blah blah"

That’s only assuming you have the same jre as me.
